reviewText: God Bless USA !!!!!!I saw this video here in my country of Trinidad and Tobago and it just blown me away ...actually the whole family was just drawn to the television.  We love when all the soldiers who served in the US came on stage and this was amazing to see such love for country.  Hats off to them and to all those who served.  This is a must have I will keep checking to see when this would available since there is none right now on Amazon...I do hope it is stocked.
summary: We love when all the soldiers who served in the US ...
